  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Named for the hammerhead genus. VA square (Voice 1) meets Wavefolder (Voice 2) at HAMMER -0.9 — full STRIFE. The cross-FM and ring modulation between a fat square wave and a folded triangle creates sub-harmonic content that no single oscillator can produce. Filter at 380 Hz with resonance 0.28 gives the bass a Formant Whisper growl. CARTILAGE macro opens the filter for a lead variant.",
